<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_174_r1l1"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> wıllıg dıenſt beuor <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> <expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Andre </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l2"><expan>Brekendorff<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . wıe der ſprech . daʒ Jm <expan>fürgebe<ex>n</ex></expan> wurd / das gut ſölt alles der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l3">von Prag ſein / darauf hab er ʒwen knecht bey der nom gehabt <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> er wölt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l4">ſein knecht <expan>vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe von <expan>Nüremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> geſchıkt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd Jm ſey auch niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l5">mer denn xxxȷ <expan>guld<ex>en</ex></expan> von dem gut <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu taıl <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> . dıe er <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>keren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l6">vnd auch darauf <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gerecht well <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> etc . das alles <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l7">Vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> daʒ wır dıe ſache an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde vom Rate alſo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l8">bracht <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jr <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd kawffleẅt dıe dıe ſache antrıft <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l9">ʒu rede geſacʒt . dıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> Jn <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> . vvıe daʒ ſıe gar ſwerlıch beſchedıgt ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l10"><expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> . vvıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> doch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnde vom Rat . mıt den Jren <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l11">gerett . vvıl der <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Andre <expan>Brekendorff<ex>er</ex></expan> . den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> alſo <expan>nachkome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
