<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l13">veyts tag ſchıerıſt . ʒu Jn kombt vnd des begert . ſo ſol er von Jn vnd ʒu Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l14">drey tag darauf geleyt <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> für ſıe vnd dıe Jren on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . denn wo wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l15">eẅch lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc . <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> vrbanj </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l16"><expan>Herdeg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>falcʒn<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Stromeır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l17">ʒur Roſen ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<div type="addressee"><p facs="#facs_174">
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l18">Dem <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>veſt<ex>en</ex></expan> Altman <expan>Kemnat<ex>er</ex></expan> pfleger ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l19">Sulcʒbach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lıeben freẅnd vnd ſwager </ab>
